e_medal":0,"score":"1628256018","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"对于“表扬型学习”以及社会认同的一些想法，还需要找到一个正确且合适的环境进行“输出”，并且不能产生依赖，如果表演过度而脱离自己实际需求，可能会催生一种“恶性竞争”的环境，而常说的“内卷”也算其中的一部分。如果对环境产生依赖很可能使人变得愈发“贪婪”，这种“贪婪”的动力往往并不是对于知识的渴望程度，而是社会环境以及需求的一种驱赶力，这种表现往往在于渴望给他人展示一种能力，也表现在给自己做“表演”试图满足自己对理想的追求，还往往伴生焦虑、“攀比”等等不良的负面情绪产生。<br><br><br>","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":302014,"user_name":"信仰年轻","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1329011,"ip_address":"","ucode":"B2BD881D25FCDD","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/14/47/73/63a3cb41.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1626019520,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"110686","content":"对的，这也是我平时写文章的重要的外部约束","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"高冷冷","uid":"2660210","ctime":1628240893,"ip_address":"","comment_id":302014,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"1626019520","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"14｜通过选择环境，来提高学习和工作效率<br>“社会助长”理论：包括“共同活动效应”和“观众效应”，前者是指在同他人共同活动时，我们的效率会提高；后者是指当他人在场旁观时，我们的效率也会提高。<br><br>尽量把任务放到有观众注视的环境之中。那就输出成博客吧，接受读者的检阅。","like_count":0,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":2660210,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/28/97/72/794537fd.jpg","nickname":"高冷冷","note":"","ucode":"DC594DF2BAC858","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":523152,"discussion_content":"对的，这也是我平时写文章的重要的外部约束","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1628240893,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":300412,"user_name":"coder.js","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1338120,"ip_address":"","ucode":"3DE173A5D23690","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/14/6b/08/15c473ef.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1625146047,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1625146047","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"“给自己做的话就会想着偷工减料，但是要给别人看的话，就会一字不漏写上” 这句还是很赞<br>","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":300322,"user_name":"🎋锋","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":2066484,"ip_address":"","ucode":"BFBF2A683377CC","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/1f/88/34/152c8d96.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1625113853,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1625113853","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"关键词：表演型学习 噪声掩盖 面向他人<br>①人类的行为具有趋同性，就像电梯间里就只有一个人向后站，在环境的压迫下他会转过身来。学习也可以利用环境，让自己趋同。<br>②利用图书馆等环境的学习相关噪音，掩盖掉自己内心不安的噪声。<br>③就像圈一以及上节课的团体约束自律，当与他人关联时，我们的责任心会大大增加。对事情的负责程度也会提升。让报班让他人给自己布置学习任务是一种解决手段。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":298831,"user_name":"ls","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1001037,"ip_address":"","ucode":"C18E208B1DFDA7","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/46/4d/161f3779.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1624341836,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1624341836","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"找到了我喜欢去图书馆看书的原因了","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":298775,"user_name":"磉盘","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1055624,"ip_address":"","ucode":"1C245991F30A73","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/1b/88/ac69f57a.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1624324383,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1624324383","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"怎么选择环境，去图书馆、自习室，因为它们比家好，可以产生“社会助长”，“印象管理”？<br>和环境保持平衡，要去有外部信息的地方，内外信息平衡，就可以专注学习了。<br>利用自己有羞耻心和利他心，找个负责联系人。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":298623,"user_name":"梓祥","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1897930,"ip_address":"","ucode":"ABA1C2DFF02A3C","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/1c/f5/ca/0b8974e9.jp